give @p written_book[written_book_content={title:"The Staff of Ages",author:"Magus Theron",pages:["Mortality… what a frustrating limitation. To be bound by the fleeting nature of existence, to succumb to the inevitable decay of the flesh… it is an insult to my genius. I sought to transcend this limitation, to defy the very laws of time itself.","And so, I created the Staff of Ages.",[{text:"Chapter 1: The Seeds of Immortality\n",bold:true},{text:"The concept was… ambitious. To tap into the very essence of time, to draw upon its energies, to… manipulate its flow. To defy aging, to extend my lifespan beyond mortal comprehension.",bold:false}],[{text:"Chapter 2: The Trials of Eternity\n",bold:true},{text:"The process was… arduous. Years of painstaking research, countless failed experiments. I delved into forbidden territories, explored the very edges of reality, risking madness itself. ",bold:false}],"But I persevered, driven by an insatiable thirst for immortality.",[{text:"Chapter 3: The Birth of Eternity\n",bold:true},{text:"And then, it happened. A surge of raw energy, a connection to the very fabric of time itself. Before my eyes, a staff of obsidian, pulsating with an eerie light, materialized in my grasp. The Staff of Ages was born.",bold:false}],[{text:"Chapter 4: A Symphony of Eternity\n",bold:true},{text:"Its effects were… profound. The flow of time around me… it slowed, almost to a standstill. My body, no longer bound by the shackles of mortality, began to rejuvenate. I felt… invincible.",bold:false}],[{text:"Chapter 5: A New Era of Dominance\n",bold:true},{text:"The Staff of Ages is a testament to my genius, a symbol of my defiance against the inevitable. Let this serve as a warning to all who dare to oppose me. I, Magus Theron, am no longer bound by the limitations of mortality. I am… eternal.",bold:false}]]}] 1